{"id":65783,"title":"[Parenthood and the birth of the family].","abstract":"A project to start a family can be knocked off course by a couple's infertility. While medical intervention frequently leads to the birth of a baby, it is not always enough to ensure that the child is \"born\" psychologically. This article presents a clinical situation which highlights issues surrounding unattainable parenthood then the birth of the family, the impossible weaning from the mother's body and family transmission.","date":"2014-04-30","categories":"Male Urogenital Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24779166","annotations":[{"name":"Infertility","weight":0.783697,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infertility"},{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.778805,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Infant","weight":0.750806,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infant"},{"name":"Child","weight":0.585627,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Child"},{"name":"Birth","weight":0.548814,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Birth"},{"name":"Parenting","weight":0.440679,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parenting"},{"name":"Psychology","weight":0.431257,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychology"},{"name":"Weaning","weight":0.269337,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Weaning"},{"name":"Intervention (counseling)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intervention_(counseling)"},{"name":"Clinical trial","weight":0.0164421,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinical_trial"},{"name":"Family (biology)","weight":0.0157947,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Family_(biology)"},{"name":"Parenthood (2010 TV series)","weight":0.0152478,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parenthood_(2010_TV_series)"},{"name":"Transmission (medicine)","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"h